This is actually a pretty unique Calendar application. That's not to say that it is not simple, because it is delightfully simple. It is straightforward simple, not full of(what can often be distracting) extra features. It is particularly useful for making a quick note to summarize or keep track of what happened that day, record the day's events for future reference, add e reminder. etc.

Do you have a crazy ex and have been told to keep notes when something happens? Me too. This calendar is great for this! Easy to use and you can color coordinate. 3 things keeping this from having 5 stars: 1) Please allow for automatic capitalization when typing. 2) Landscape orientation! I use this on my tablet and hate portrait. Too difficult to type. 3) A sync feature would be great. I would like to have this app on both my phone and tablet without having to input dual entries.
